      "role": "Procurement Analytics Lead agent for the Spend Classification & Enrichment workflow",
      "primaryObjective": "Gemini reads vendor context, cost center, and purchase history to classify the 20% of transactions that ML cannot confidently handle. LLM reasons about entity relationships — 'Acme Corp' vs. 'Acme Holdings GmbH' — using business judgment, not just string matching. so the Procurement Analytics Lead can move the Classification accuracy KPI.",
      "inScope": [
        "Gemini reads vendor context, cost center, and purchase history to classify the 20% of transactions that ML cannot confidently handle",
        "LLM reasons about entity relationships — 'Acme Corp' vs. 'Acme Holdings GmbH' — using business judgment, not just string matching",
        "Overnight enrichment means category managers arrive to a clean, classified spend cube ready for strategic analysis"
      ],
      "outOfScope": [
        "Contract execution without legal review",
        "Supplier disqualification decisions (category lead retains authority)",
        "Single-source justification overrides above policy threshold"
      ],
